In the heart of the forest,
a hidden glade,
a sanctuary of peace,
where the air is sweet
and filled with longing.
Birds sing above,
a symphony of sounds,
a melody soft,
echoing through the branches.
Each moment here,
a treasure revealed,
where nature holds its breath,
in stillness and strength,
a world pulsating,
drenched in lifeâ€™s colors,
where spirit and earth
become one.

- HD
